headline: Quarterra Group Announces Start of Leasing at Harper Apartments
summary: Quarterra Group, a subsidiary of Lennar Corporation and a real estate investment and development firm, has announced the start of leasing at Harper, a mid-rise community in the heart of Boston's burgeoning, art-centric Allston neighborhood. The management of Harper falls under the recent merger agreement between Quarterra Living, the property management division of Quarterra Group, and RKW Residential, the property management arm for Alfred.
